# Testing

- Rust: crop bounds, resize modes, encode round-trip, maxSizeKB
- TS: batch option merge, error mapping
- Fixtures in `tests/fixtures/` — keep small (<100KB each)
- Visual/hash regression optional; do not commit >1MB images
